<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Inscape</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-05-23 23:33:25</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Well, to waste time...i do camp Dragnor's for the "named" spawns.  I've killed Bilge 6 times and fought him 7 times.<BR>
<BR>
He drops REED belt as a common or rare Pearl Kedge Totem.<BR>
I beat him with a bit of a tussle as a 40 Ranger...and would<BR>
not like to meet him without full health and mana.<BR>
<BR>
I have never found him in the same place or traveling in the same direction.  His spawn times have been quite random<BR>
with an occassional propensity to spawn the following day at about the same time(i've seen this twice and heard about<BR>
it once).  <BR>
<BR>
The other Goblin with the cleric item is Dwigus Lowater and<BR>
I can't beat him....but is blue to me.  The other rare<BR>
spawns are easy(Squallslither, Baracle Bones, Flotsam, and<BR>
Jetsam).<BR>
<BR>
I have traded a REED for Ykesha Short Sword....  :)<BR>
<BR>
If you camp him....bring bat wings for levitate and plenty of bait for your fishing skill(+/- some beverages).<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
