<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Koroth</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-16 09:59:57</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Wow.  People sure raped that Neo guy.  I've never really camped the reed belt or care about it.  Just not one to actively camp rare stuff.  However it seems to have brought good luck.  In the last year and a half I've killed Bilge about 20 to 25 times.  Has had the Reed Belt about 90% of the time.  Usually trade it for 10k plat value in trade.  Never sold one yet.  So far I've only SEEN him spawn 2 times.  Both times a little ways from the Goblin Camp and both times I didn't have my character to kill him as I was camping goblin lords and such for xp.  Other times just happened across him on the way to Kedge and Unrest.  I'm guessing he probably spawns most anywhere.  I have lost him from target and tracking 5 or 6 times.  He seems to like running out to that middle island.  And I think the Dwarven Plate guy there woops his butt.</font></td></tr></table>
