<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: bruja</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-07 01:00:25</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Ok, heres the skinny on the norraths most wanted goblin. he is actually quite easy to kill as a result of a glitch, but still the so called superman rogue neotheo can still shove it, because he cant do it asa  rogue even with the trick. there with that said, i shall reveal the secret to your veryown shiney brand-spankin new reed belt. if you are lucky enough to come across this little blue skin, make sure you have full mana; because he is a shaman. then root him right away and hightail it to the high ground. as i stood there waiting for him to come in range ihe never showed, so i figured someone took him. i went down, and low and behold an arrow doth fly by my head. now you see once you get far enough away something clicks, and instead of the VoS and Scourge youve been expecting, arrows are your treat. ;-). being a necro i stood there and stacked so many dot's on his blue-skinned behind that his corpse was eaten away after it had burt from tha blood boiling off. so now friends there is a way for you lvl 35's to get one of the most covetted items in the land.<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
