<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Bah, dont camp...pleh, i camped poor ol' Bilge and his buddy for 13 or 14 hours today on Bertoxxulous.  Dwigus conned yellow to me at 34 as a druid, yet i whupped him 3 or 4 times. Then FINALLY Bilge spawned.  I was downstairs getting a drink, and i knew i had competition out there so i hightailed it following him on tracking.  Anyways, both Dwigus and Bilge seem to have set points to run around and sit down. Lots of times, underwater, and they criss-cross the lake a lot. Best thing i did was root and DOT, and walk away. BTW he was a blue con to me. Anyways, so i come back, and i see a lvl 58 druid sitting there about to take him from me, so i pop 1 DD on him and she took him out.  Oddly enough, dont ask me how unless Bilge is a wuss on HP's, but i got the kill and the Belt, so i was happy. Funny thing was, as usual, i was accused as a KSer...i said look at the lvl's, and the conversation w/ that person quickly ended.  Anyways, he can be camped, you just need a massive ammount of patience...my brain is throbbing right now, so i must go :(</font></td></tr></table>
